         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>To Menches, komogrammateus of Kerkeosiris, from Horos, son of Petechon, king's farmer of the area of the same (village). Inasmuch as I am living with ]thonis, daughter of T[Ö]os, from the area of the same village in accordance with an Egyptian boarding contract, and as I am providing the same all the necessities according to the ability of my resourcesÖ</ab>
